column2: SELECT TOP #   obj.run, obj.camCol, str(obj.field, #) as field,  str(obj.rowc, #, #) as rowc, str(obj.colc, #, #) as colc,  str(dbo.fObj(obj.objId), #) as id,   str(obj.psfMag_g - #*obj.extinction_g, #, #) as g,  str(obj.psfMag_r - #*obj.extinction_r, #, #) as r,  str(obj.psfMag_i - #*obj.extinction_i, #, #) as i,  str(obj.psfMag_z - #*obj.extinction_z, #, #) as z,  str(#*distance, #, #) as D,  dbo.fField(neighborObjId) as nfield,  str(dbo.fObj(neighborObjId), #) as nid FROM  (SELECT obj.objId,  run, camCol, field, rowc, colc,  psfMag_u, extinction_u,  psfMag_g, extinction_g,  psfMag_r, extinction_r,  psfMag_i, extinction_i,  psfMag_z, extinction_z,  NN.neighborObjId, NN.distance  FROM PhotoObj as obj  JOIN neighbors as NN on obj.objId = NN.objId  WHERE  #*NN.distance between # and # and  NN.mode = # and NN.neighborMode = # and  run = # and camCol = # and  obj.type = # and (obj.flags & #) = # and  nchild = # and obj.psfMag_i < # and  (g - r between # and # and r - i between # and #)  ) as obj  JOIN PhotoObj as nobj on nobj.objId = obj.neighborObjId  WHERE   nobj.run = obj.run and  (abs(obj.psfMag_g - nobj.psfMag_g) < # or  abs(obj.psfMag_r - nobj.psfMag_r) < # or  abs(obj.psfMag_i - nobj.psfMag_i) < #)
